name: .DMSA File Extension
summary: Learn about .DMSA files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Project file created by Music Disc Creator, a program used to create music compilations; stores project information, such as references to audio files, sound edits, transitions, and track information.

content: DMSA files are used to save and load music compilation projects. They can be used to export music to personal media players, or they may be exported to various audio file formats, including .MP3 and .WAV.
NOTE: Music Disc Creator is bundled as part of the Roxio Creator multimedia suite.
